Summary: UFO in picture when shuttle landing
trends: There have been 112 other sightings in Orlando
There were no other sightings in Orlando on or around October 18th 2002
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting DetailsTaking pictures of the shuttle landing at KSC as the shuttle came in from the south about to land. The shuttle is just seconds from landing and about to drop the landing gear. Picture taken from launch complex 39 looking west as the shuttle glided in. One of the pictures had an object that appears to be above and just west of the shuttle. The object was not seen while viewing the shuttle, only when examining the picture. The object only appeared in one of the photo's taken. We did not see any chase aircraft.
